    <h3>New Ways to Sort Event Broker Services in PubSub+ Cloud</h3>
    <p>The way users can sort existing <MadCap:variable name="Product-Names.cloud_product_short"/> event broker services has been improved.
Upon navigating to the Messaging Services screen in the cloud console, users will be able to sort through the list of available services based on Service Type, Cloud Region, User, and Creation Date, making it easier to find the desired services. 
</p>
    <p>
      <img class="solacethumbnail" src="../../../Images/Cloud/rn-sort-event-broker-services.png" alt=""/>
    </p>
    <p class="Note">To clean up the interface, the service creation button will no longer appear in the list of available services unless the user chooses to sort by “None”. Users can still start services by selecting the Create Service navigation button in green at the top of the screen. </p>
