    <h3>Create Services With 250 Connections</h3>
    <p>You can now create enterprise event broker services with 250 connections. This is for use cases when you don’t need the 1000 connections of our previously lowest scale enterprise service, but unlike developer services, still want your service to be HA and have configurable network throughput and storage.</p>
    <p>If your account is configured with the appropriate limits, you can start a 250-connection service just as you would with any of the other services, Upon service creation for enterprise services, you’ll notice the connection slider now starts at 250 and goes up to 100K.</p>
    <p>
      <img class="solacethumbnail" src="../../../Images/Historic Release Notes_7-2-2020/PubSub Cloud Release Notes_2.png" alt=""/>
    </p>
